{"tid":1676643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10點鳩叫點解唔升級 可加埋文宣同閂燈5分鐘","createTime":"2019-10-26T14:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T06:59:04.000Z","uid":83993,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1cbf6fe536be0dd529c8e0c11e7c5a17169b5d0b","tid":1676643,"uid":83993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:55:08.000Z","msg":"1. 宜家D人成日話差佬襯手足貼連儂牆果陣鳩拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以唔敢出黎做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過其實唔一定連儂牆先可以做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10點鐘鳩嗌 都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n建議鳩叫果陣可以有固定既口號有對白寫好哂 而唔係隨心想嗌咩就嗌咩<br />\n然後最尾果句口號係為果個星期既活動做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如下面呢張圖可以加 &quot;10月27 下就3點 尖沙咀 遊行&quot; 或者再簡單D &quot;星期日 尖咀見&quot;:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vQmbt8p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvQmbt8p.jpg&h=eb513678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 如果鳩嗌可以加埋閂燈 成個屋苑多人跟果陣 就會變死城一個<br />\n如果有傳媒影到D屋苑每晚變死城 話唔定會令到其他屋苑都跟<br />\n如果真係可以每日全港有5分鐘變死城 係一個極靚既畫面 一定上國際媒體既報導<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 十點鐘鳩叫對keep住成個運動好重要<br />\n每日Keep住鳩嗌係可以Keep住大家團火 一去休息 團火就冇架啦<br />\n宜家無可否認係少左人去活動<br />\n所以要靠十點鐘鳩叫 叫返醒大家團火"},{"pid":"3b98329b38f703f93e44530779dfa22bf9272f43","tid":1676643,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:55:51.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},{"pid":"fc1d8f17b3458f620c3a68dd63e101ef84236a4c","tid":1676643,"uid":83993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:56:12.000Z","msg":"仲有樣野好想講<br />\n大定見到有用既post唔該推post比更多人見到<br />\n唔好剩係比正皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca19103ba3f5cdfa5816fae76468252ff46727b","tid":1676643,"uid":274538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:56:51.000Z","msg":"聽日見！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C37qKAa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC37qKAa.jpg&h=3e3afe9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E3JmhVb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE3JmhVb.jpg&h=3ab5f3b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5NPXAGS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5NPXAGS.jpg&h=d3849302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DTLPrOy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDTLPrOy.gif&h=a0152400&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6407c230dfec0ab07634c433449de57c4dbc8b65","tid":1676643,"uid":83993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3b98329b38f703f93e44530779dfa22bf9272f43","tid":1676643,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:55:51.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:57:06.000Z","msg":"其實可以加埋黃店list入去每日鳩叫既口號果到都得喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34b8c80ee2a9d6a36d21de1e55eadb079647474","tid":1676643,"uid":164190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:57:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"21af8530014f0cd17b40a6127924a3a111ed3f81","tid":1676643,"uid":7738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:58:54.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"435a8ebeb18a7f6a01a308ea